I"ì<p><a href="https://www.elgato.com/en/news/elgato-avea-transform-your-home">Elgato Avea</a> is a Bluetooth light bulb that is no longer supported by the manufacturer. The <code>avea</code> integration allows you to control all your Avea bulbs with Home Assistant.</p>
<h3>Configuration</h3>
<p>To enable Avea, add the following lines to your <code>configuration.yaml</code> file:</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml"># Example configuration.yaml entry
light:
  - platform: avea
</code></pre>
